# Dataset cache (CC BY-NC 4.0 — not redistributable inside the repo)
data/
*.json.cache
# Eval database (large, regenerable, license-tainted by derivation)
eval.db
eval.db-wal
eval.db-shm
.workspace/
# Dataset commit lock — committed copy may differ from local; gitignore the local
# resolved lock to avoid noisy diffs between runs. The README freezes the SHA used
# for any published number.
dataset.lock.json
# Full-run output kept out of git (we only commit aggregate summaries)
full-run.json
# Note: dry-run-sample.json IS committed (10-row plumbing artefact, no LoCoMo verbatim
# beyond chunk-ID strings).
# Python cross-bench harness outputs:
# - results/RESULTS-SMOKE-*.json + results/RESULTS-FULL-*.json (aggregate, committed)
# - results/results-*.jsonl (per-record raw, contains LoCoMo question/answer strings
#   verbatim — NOT committed due to CC BY-NC license; reproducible via run-bench.sh)
results/results-*.jsonl
results/adapter-stderr.log
__pycache__/
*.pyc
